But on the whole I've been a saint

513
00:41:13,805 --> 00:41:18,225
To those poor unfortunate souls

514
00:41:18,910 --> 00:41:20,690
Now, here's the deal.

515
00:41:21,012 --> 00:41:25,582
I will make you a potion that will
turn you into a human for three days.

516
00:41:26,284 --> 00:41:28,534
Got that? Three days.

517
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:31,350
Now, listen, this is important.

518
00:41:31,756 --> 00:41:33,836
Before the sun sets
on the third day,

519
00:41:34,192 --> 00:41:38,092
you've got to get dear old princie
to fall in love with you.

520
00:41:38,696 --> 00:41:41,246
That is, he's got to kiss you.

521
00:41:41,666 --> 00:41:46,466
Not just any kiss,
the kiss of true love.

522
00:41:47,205 --> 00:41:50,485
If he does kiss you
before the sun sets on the third day,

523
00:41:50,975 --> 00:41:54,485
you'll remain human permanently.

524
00:41:55,013 --> 00:41:58,083
But if he doesn't,
you'll turn back into a mermaid

525
00:41:58,683 --> 00:42:02,253
and you belong to me.

526
00:42:02,787 --> 00:42:05,276
No, Ariel.

527
00:42:05,690 --> 00:42:07,770
Have we got a deal?

528
00:42:08,126 --> 00:42:10,116
If l become human,

529
00:42:10,461 --> 00:42:12,890
I'll never be
with my father or sisters again.

530
00:42:13,297 --> 00:42:15,317
That's right.

531
00:42:15,666 --> 00:42:18,536
But you'll have your man.

532
00:42:20,405 --> 00:42:23,885
Life's full of tough choices, isn't it?

533
00:42:26,310 --> 00:42:30,060
Oh, and there is one more thing.

534
00:42:30,648 --> 00:42:32,898
We haven't discussed
the subject of payment.

535
00:42:33,284 --> 00:42:35,064
You can't get something for nothing.

536
00:42:35,386 --> 00:42:37,556
- But I don't have any...
- I'm not asking much.

537
00:42:37,922 --> 00:42:41,582
Just a token really, a trifle.
You'll never even miss it.

538
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:46,060
What I want from you is your voice.

539
00:42:47,432 --> 00:42:50,392
- My voice?
- You've got it, sweetcakes.

540
00:42:50,868 --> 00:42:54,058
No more talking, singing. Zip.

541
00:42:54,572 --> 00:42:56,322
But without my voice, how can I...

542
00:42:56,641 --> 00:43:00,041
You'll have your looks,
your pretty face.

543
00:43:00,678 --> 00:43:05,188
And don't underestimate
the importance of body language.

544
00:43:06,751 --> 00:43:09,301
The men up there
don't like a lot of blabber

545
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:11,970
They think a girl who gossips is a bore

546
00:43:12,356 --> 00:43:14,726
On land it's much preferred
for ladies not to say a word

547
00:43:15,126 --> 00:43:17,316
And, after all, dear
What is idle prattle for?

548
00:43:17,695 --> 00:43:18,805
Come on.

549
00:43:19,030 --> 00:43:21,550
They're not all that impressed
with conversation

550
