True gentlemen avoid it
when they can

551
00:43:24,669 --> 00:43:26,009
But they dote and swoon and fawn

552
00:43:26,270 --> 00:43:27,670
On a lady who's withdrawn

553
00:43:27,939 --> 00:43:30,019
It's she who holds her tongue
who gets her man

554
00:43:30,374 --> 00:43:33,774
Come on,
you poor unfortunate soul

555
00:43:34,312 --> 00:43:36,892
Go ahead, make your choice

556
00:43:37,315 --> 00:43:39,805
I'ma very busy woman
and I haven't got all day

557
00:43:40,218 --> 00:43:42,877
lt won't cost much
Just your voice

558
00:43:43,321 --> 00:43:45,341
Ya poor, unfortunate soul

559
00:43:45,690 --> 00:43:48,240
It's sad, but true

560
00:43:48,659 --> 00:43:50,849
If you want to cross a bridge,
my sweet, you've got to pay the toll

561
00:43:51,229 --> 00:43:54,098
Take a gulp and take a breath
and go ahead and sign the scroll

562
00:43:54,532 --> 00:43:56,492
Flotsam, Jetsam
Now I've got her, boys

563
00:43:56,801 --> 00:44:00,111
The boss is on a roll

564
00:44:00,738 --> 00:44:03,397
This poor, unfortunate

565
00:44:03,808 --> 00:44:08,638
Soul

566
00:44:10,815 --> 00:44:12,275
Beluga, sevruga

567
00:44:12,550 --> 00:44:16,390
Come, winds of the Caspian Sea

568
00:44:16,988 --> 00:44:20,178
Larynxis, glossitis
Et max laryngitis

569
00:44:20,691 --> 00:44:23,761
La voce to me

570
00:44:24,262 --> 00:44:26,312
Now, sing.

571
00:44:32,170 --> 00:44:33,920
Keep singing.

572
00:45:34,799 --> 00:45:39,189
That voice.
I can't get it out of my head.

573
00:45:39,870 --> 00:45:43,350
I've looked everywhere, Max.
Where could she be?

574
00:46:02,727 --> 00:46:07,087
Well, look at what
the catfish dragged in.

575
00:46:08,366 --> 00:46:10,146
Look at ya.

576
00:46:10,468 --> 00:46:13,368
There's somethin’ different.
Don't tell me.

577
00:46:13,838 --> 00:46:16,238
I got it. It's your hairdo, right?

578
00:46:16,641 --> 00:46:18,451
You've been usin' the dinglehopper.

579
00:46:20,278 --> 00:46:23,298
No? Well, let me see.

580
00:46:23,781 --> 00:46:25,531
New seashells?

581
