625
00:49:26,230 --> 00:49:28,570
No. You need help?

626
00:49:29,533 --> 00:49:31,343
Careful. Careful, easy.

627
00:49:32,870 --> 00:49:35,420
You must have
really been through something.

628
00:49:35,840 --> 00:49:37,770
Don't worry. I'll help you.

629
00:49:38,108 --> 00:49:39,808
Come on. You'll be OK.

630
00:49:48,352 --> 00:49:50,402
Washed up from a shipwreck.

631
00:49:51,856 --> 00:49:53,636
The poor thing.

632
00:49:53,958 --> 00:49:56,828
We'll have you feeling better
in no time.

633
00:49:59,997 --> 00:50:03,596
I'll just get this washed for you.

634
00:50:08,372 --> 00:50:10,361
You must have at least
heard about this girl.

635
00:50:10,708 --> 00:50:12,408
- No.
- Gertrude says...

636
00:50:12,710 --> 00:50:15,750
When has Gertrude
ever gotten anything right?

637
00:50:16,247 --> 00:50:17,946
- Really.
- Madam, please...

638
00:50:18,249 --> 00:50:21,269
