You need to get out.

701
00:54:52,456 --> 00:54:54,386
Do something. Have a life.

702
00:54:54,725 --> 00:54:56,424
- Get your mind off...
- Easy, Grim.

703
00:54:56,727 --> 00:54:59,567
It's not a bad idea,
if she's interested.

704
00:55:00,030 --> 00:55:01,230
Well, what do ya say?

705
00:55:01,465 --> 00:55:04,185
Would you like to join me
on a tour of my kingdom tomorrow?

706
00:55:04,635 --> 00:55:09,175
Wonderful. Now, let's eat
before this crab wanders off my plate.

707
00:55:19,316 --> 00:55:21,066
Come here, boy.

708
00:55:37,067 --> 00:55:39,817
This has got to be, without a doubt,

709
00:55:40,270 --> 00:55:44,220
the single most humiliating day
of my life.

710
00:55:44,842 --> 00:55:49,672
l hope that you appreciate
what I go through for you, young lady.

711
00:55:50,380 --> 00:55:53,920
Now, we got to make a plan
to get that boy to kiss you.

712
00:55:54,451 --> 00:55:58,931
Tomorrow when he takes you
for that ride, you gotta look your best.

713
00:55:59,723 --> 00:56:03,673
You gotta bat your eyes, like this.

714
00:56:04,261 --> 00:56:08,921
You gotta pucker up your lips,
like this.

715
00:56:19,610 --> 00:56:24,240
You are hopeless, child.
You know that?

716
00:56:24,948 --> 00:56:28,138
Completely hopeless.

717
00:56:37,094 --> 00:56:38,324
Any sign of them?

718
00:56:38,562 --> 00:56:41,281
No, Your Majesty.
We searched everywhere.

719
00:56:41,732 --> 00:56:44,662
We've found no trace
of your daughter or Sebastian.

720
00:56:45,135 --> 00:56:48,855
Keep looking. Leave no shell unturned,
no coral unexplored.

721
00:56:49,439 --> 00:56:53,098
Let no one in this kingdom sleep
until she's safe at home.

722
00:56:53,677 --> 00:56:55,427
Yes, sire.

723
00:56:58,282 --> 00:57:00,032
