738
00:59:23,727 --> 00:59:26,477
Percussion.

739
00:59:26,930 --> 00:59:30,149
Strings. Winds.

740
00:59:30,667 --> 00:59:32,687
Words.

741
00:59:33,036 --> 00:59:35,586
There you see her

742
00:59:36,006 --> 00:59:38,846
Sitting there across the way

743
00:59:39,309 --> 00:59:41,419
She don't got a lot to say

744
00:59:41,778 --> 00:59:45,408
But there's something about her

745
00:59:45,982 --> 00:59:48,971
And you don't know why
but you're dyin’ to try

746
00:59:49,453 --> 00:59:51,183
You wanna kiss the girl

747
00:59:51,488 --> 00:59:53,857
Did you hear something?

748
00:59:54,257 --> 00:59:56,687
Yes, you want her

749
00:59:57,094 --> 01:00:00,314
Look at her
You know you do

750
01:00:00,831 --> 01:00:02,531
Possible she want you too

751
01:00:02,833 --> 01:00:06,553
There is one way to ask her

752
01:00:07,137 --> 01:00:08,977
It don't take a word

753
01:00:09,306 --> 01:00:12,996
Not a single word
Go on and kiss the girl

754
01:00:13,577 --> 01:00:14,917
Sing with me now.

