757
01:00:22,486 --> 01:00:24,915
Sha-la-la-la-la-la
Ain't that sad?

758
01:00:25,322 --> 01:00:26,662
Ain't ita shame?

759
01:00:26,923 --> 01:00:30,493
Too bad he gonna miss the girl

760
01:00:31,061 --> 01:00:32,991
l feel really bad not knowing your name.

761
01:00:33,330 --> 01:00:36,840
Maybe I could guess. Is it Mildred?

